metadata.name: Through the eye of Love
metadata.description:
FREEISH HOLIDAY MINT 0.001ETH  
Appreciation animation piece bringing one of my biggest wishes for you and hummanity: to be able to always see through the eyes of love and compassion. No war, no duality, no suffering among us. May love be our only path. 

NO LIMIT PER WALLET  
Top 3 token holders get colorful edition airdrop!
